Server Configuration
PORT=5000

MongoDB Connection
Replace with your own MongoDB connection string
MONGO_URI=mongodb+srv://<user>:<password>@cluster0.mongodb.net/ai-roadmap?retryWrites=true&w=majority

Google Gemini API Key
IMPORTANT: Keep this secret and do not commit to version control
GEMINI_API_KEY=PASTE_YOUR_GEMINI_API_KEY_HERE

Firebase Admin SDK Service Account
Paste the entire contents of your Firebase service account JSON file here.
It should be a single line. Make sure to handle newlines correctly if copying.
FIREBASE_SERVICE_ACCOUNT=